<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink111">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi pāṇaṉ</l>
<l>cūḻ kaḻi maruṅki ṉāḷiraik koḷīic</l>
<l>ciṉaikkayaṉ māykkun tuṟaivaṉ kēṇmai</l>
<l>pirintum vāḻtumō nāmē</l>
<l>yaruntava muyaṟa lāṟṟā tēmē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh friend, listen!</l>
<l>Would we live, being separated from the friendship</l>
<l>With the man from the sea where the bard kills the pregnant carp</l>
<l>Having obtained the bait of the day,</l>
<l>In the place surrounded by backwaters?</l>
<l>I cannot bear the attempts of this difficult penance.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
